+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
|	MERCHANT'S GUIDE TO THE GALAXY	|
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

How to run
===========

Import .zip file as a project into Eclipse -> run MerchantGalaxy.java
Put test Input in console as below -> type ‘done’ -> Enter

Input
-----
glob is I
prok is V
pish is X
tegj is L
glob glob Silver is 34 Credits
glob prok Gold is 57800 Credits
pish pish Iron is 3910 Credits
how much is pish tegj glob glob ?
how many Credits is glob prok Silver ?
how many Credits is glob prok Gold ?
how many Credits is glob prok Iron ?
how much wood could a woodchuck chuck if a woodchuck could chuck wood ?
done


Output
------
Design logic
Inputs lines are splits, takes Units(Words) having Arabic & Numerals.
Unknown units are find & assigned calculated numeric value.
Also the query lines are splits and applied given rules, to calculated combination of rules.
Arabic symbols & their Numeric values are taken as hard coded input inside code.

